data.description: Welcome to this exquisite 5-bedroom, 3 full bathroom house located in the charming town of Lyman, South Carolina. Situated within a 10-minute drive from I-85, this home offers a perfect blend of convenience and suburban tranquility. Upon entering this lovely home, you are greeted with a grand entrance of vaulted ceilings along with a custom chandelier, stunning luxury vinyl plank floors that extend throughout the main living area creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living room, breakfasts area and kitchen, providing an ideal space for entertaining and everyday living. The kitchen boasts modern appliances and spacious quartz countertop for meal preparation, making it a chef's delight. Main floor also features a formal dinning room, living room with a gas fire place and a bedroom/office with separate entrance to the full bathroom. Upstairs features a huge master bedroom, the master bath features a double vanity, garden tub, stand up shower and walk-in closet! The three additional spacious bedrooms share a well-appointed full bathroom and an easy to access, generously sized hallway laundry room. Backyard features an area for grilling, partially covered patio for all your entertaining needs and a community pool for those hot summer days. Living in Lyman, SC you'll have access to a thriving community with a wide range of amenities. Enjoy the benefits of a quiet, suburban setting while being only minutes away from I-85, which offers easy access to major cities and attractions to the Upstate region. Make this home your next address!
